Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:07.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.84,0:00:11.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,最后成了件大工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.74,0:00:15.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不感到怀念吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.52,0:00:19.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到会把这个拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.42,0:00:25.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会不知道这是多么危险的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.84,0:00:27.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.37,0:00:29.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在看护着它
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.79,0:00:37.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,正因如此才会成那些孩子今后旅途上需要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.14,0:00:39.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因果循环啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.85,0:00:42.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我不这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.93,0:00:46.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管人类看起来像是重复同样的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.06,0:00:49.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但因果绝不是循环的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.22,0:00:51.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是螺旋般的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.44,0:00:57.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那些孩子不一定会选如你我一样的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.66,0:01:01.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.18,0:01:10.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我的灵力竟如此脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:13.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,结界轻而易举就被击破了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.01,0:01:20.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要为我而战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.84,0:01:22.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但无论哪条路我已经
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.22,0:01:26.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,正因如此才要心平气和地战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.10,0:01:29.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.44,0:01:31.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会忘记你的真心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.54,0:01:33.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我的老友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.80,0:01:51.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,至少最后能再一次看到你那羞涩的笑容
Comment: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:25.34,DefaultSub,,0,0,0,,/-------START--------/
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.34,0:03:26.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:27.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:31.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才一瞬间好像感受到了师傅的念
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:35.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,渴望快点得到芙罗拉的夸奖而按捺不住了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:40.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女见习却能退治恶鬼定会成为这里的新传说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:44.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:49.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我能做到的只是堵住兽鬼的巢穴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:52.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然召唤出了巨大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:54.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,却不能好好使用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:56.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,徒然让损害扩大而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:03:59.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我还不成熟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:04.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我好感动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:08.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 你的眼睛有点可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.51,0:04:11.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,抓到了什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:16.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,老实说我还不知道他们是不是我的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.06,0:04:19.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:24.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.44,0:04:28.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.85,0:04:31.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在那个寺院伤口没有愈合吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.70,0:04:34.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:37.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,果然伤口已经愈合了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:39.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 伤口非常深
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:43.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,肉体的伤口确实愈合了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:47.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但幽体的伤口还留在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:50.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,放任不管就会不断衰弱下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:53.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,早晚会让肉体的伤口再次裂开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.74,0:04:56.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会 能救他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.84,0:05:00.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,尽快抬到洋馆 让他服下师傅的灵药的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.80,0:05:02.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大家来帮我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:08.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我无大碍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:12.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是一时没站稳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:17.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,肩膀倒是可以借你一用 虽然我不情愿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:18.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:23.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,幽体之伤即精神之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.90,0:05:26.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,应该会有法忍受的剧痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:29.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一般的人都无法保持意识清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:31.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.28,0:05:35.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我们逃出以后在那里到底遇到了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.68,0:05:40.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个伤应该不是兽鬼弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:45.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我施上去的护符也不知什么时候被抹消了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.53,0:05:49.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只是用它揍了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.44,0:05:54.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,用这东西揍了自认为是天使的怪物一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:59.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这种 这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:03.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,区区人类竟有和那种高位灵体战斗的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:06.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那把剑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.98,0:06:11.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不断斩杀幽体而获得此种力量的剑的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:12.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:17.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要因被预言的奇迹而蒙蔽双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.18,0:06:22.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,请看看眼前的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.26,0:06:26.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.68,0:06:32.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 这种灵气的流动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.57,0:06:34.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,森林的深处
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.38,0:06:36.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是洋馆的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.12,0:06:39.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,森林的结界消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:43.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.54,0:06:46.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法尔纳塞和卡思嘉在这里等着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:47.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:49.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是剩下的兽鬼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:51.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有棘手的东西在洋馆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:54.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,兽鬼根本不能比
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.09,0:06:55.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,婆婆有危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.72,0:06:58.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:11.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,师 师博大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.86,0:07:14.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:19.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你们快拦住她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:29.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不会错 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:33.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,使徒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.43,0:07:45.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋从哪冒出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:55.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 有人类闯入这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:57.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女的同伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.92,0:08:00.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我很痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:02.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要挥动那把大剑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.70,0:08:07.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,却摇摇晃晃地 真不像话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.84,0:08:19.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是你 为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:24.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我和这个洋馆的主人交情很深
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:25.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,交情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:30.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 所以那时会在兽鬼的巢穴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.58,0:08:32.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:36.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些使徒不配知我名讳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.11,0:08:41.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我只会说给向5名天使复仇之人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:43.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么胡言乱语
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:47.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等等这样啊 我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.87,0:08:50.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我等之主转生之时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:53.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,于该地现身的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:55.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.09,0:08:59.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我也知道你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.30,0:09:04.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我们主人的祭品 那个幸存下来的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.14,0:09:07.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:12.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,竟会在这里遇到你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.69,0:09:16.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是命运吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:17.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,左德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:20.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么在这
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:24.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说你们的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:26.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不问也知
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:30.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,命定为主君的在这世上只有一人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:35.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,左德大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.09,0:09:37.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.40,0:09:41.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就委派给我古伦贝路多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.88,0:09:43.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:45.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:48.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我听过你的传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:51.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,虽是一介凡人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:54.19,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,却是从他的蚀中生还的豪杰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:56.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.42,0:10:02.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,人多势众攻打一个在如此偏僻的森林隐居的老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:07.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,实在有损武人的名誉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:12.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但却是向鹰示忠的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:17.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,于是本人才要求与他们同行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:22.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到会遇到你这样的武者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:27.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,着沉重的步伐来到此地也值了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:31.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格里菲斯的命令 为何他要把婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.60,0:10:35.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我古伦贝路多 特作为鹰之团的一介武夫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.38,0:10:39.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,和黑色剑士单挑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:40.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:43.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.28,0:10:46.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才他说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:50.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么鹰之团
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:53.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:10:59.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,伊斯多洛先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:02.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么呀 魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:03.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法怎么了 魔法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:07.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我的心很乱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:09.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,使不出魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:10.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:16.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个快从这里出去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:17.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,塞尔彼高
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:21.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不能用你的羽毛羽毛撢子做点什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.10,0:11:24.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊 只会把火势增大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.86,0:11:28.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅大人 你在哪 回答我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.49,0:11:30.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,史尔基
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.87,0:11:33.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:37.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好好听着 我的嫡传弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.10,0:11:40.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,把那个交给黑色剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:42.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是 莫非是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.26,0:11:44.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,到底发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.84,0:11:46.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:50.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快些 可怕的敌人迫近了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.72,0:11:53.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去剑士先生会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.44,0:11:56.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但这样的话师傅你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.56,0:11:58.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.58,0:12:00.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.19,0:12:03.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那一刻已来临
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:04.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:09.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这样 这样太残忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:10.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,应该更宁静地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:13.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不是被这样的火包围
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.02,0:12:17.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我本就背负的这样的罪业
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:23.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,人类违背时间的法则延命至今是多么罪孽深重
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.52,0:12:28.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,身为魔法师的你应该清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:30.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.96,0:12:34.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 果然还是太寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:42.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我 不管是阳光下的膝枕 还是和格雷姆们的午茶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.15,0:12:45.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,所有 所有都会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:47.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,都要被烧毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:50.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,史尔基
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.46,0:13:08.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,多么凶狠的一击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.05,0:13:12.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,明明还是人类的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:15.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,力量却高于一般的使徒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:21.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你们有什么资格 自称鹰之团啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.22,0:13:36.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙 刚才乱来那么一下裂了好几根骨头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.30,0:13:39.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起的剑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:44.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,吃了我两战锤竟然没有断
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.06,0:13:48.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你这算什么战斗方式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:53.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,连抵抗都不行 只是一直被打飞不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.01,0:13:55.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,站着说话不腰疼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.60,0:13:57.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,连甲胄都没有赤膊上阵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:02.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,火龙老大也是真喜欢这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.62,0:14:06.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也赶紧做完工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.90,0:14:08.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,把魔女的脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:11.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:14.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你他妈的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:16.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,躲开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.70,0:14:20.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我来做这家伙的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:22.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也忍不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:23.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙把同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:29.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是命令 你们把魔女的脑袋带过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:31.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,别拖拖拉拉的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.76,0:14:39.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,正打得火热的时候 你要去追女人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:41.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一点也不像你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:47.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,对你来说 战斗才是一切 不死者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.56,0:14:54.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要会错意 能阻止你的只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:56.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:15:02.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都和平时不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.37,0:15:07.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 喔 都是小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:09.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女的弟子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:14.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事 刚退冶了兽鬼 这次是怪人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:16.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是 使徒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:21.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们不想死就告诉我魔女在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.43,0:15:24.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不过就是说了也会被烧死罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:37.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:38.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不赶紧跑出去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:42.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很残酷 但是要去救芙罗拉的话我们也
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:44.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,去宝物库
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.08,0:15:47.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那里有必须交给格斯的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.88,0:15:50.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.71,0:15:53.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这就是师傅的愿望的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:59.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人是不是我的命运 我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:04.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是现在能救他的只有我这个魔法师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:08.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只有身为灵树森林的魔女芙罗拉的弟子的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.24,0:16:10.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,才能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:13.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.56,0:16:17.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要给的东西 是那个护符吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:20.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,对 但不止这些
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:23.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅上了护符的咒物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:26.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,危险且强力的某种咒物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.55,0:16:33.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:39.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的是那个黑色剑士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:42.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,听说打败了不少使徒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:46.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,和那个不死的左德打的不分上下的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.38,0:16:47.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的宿敌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.16,0:16:50.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是这种窝囊废吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.34,0:16:51.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:57.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,左德大人运气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:17:00.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,能遇上那种劲敌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:05.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,对武者来说 战场即是圣地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:09.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,置于死地而后生才是本分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:16.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你好像不配武者的荣耀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:20.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个怪物现在装什么武者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:22.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,自我陶醉的混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.93,0:17:30.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,作为战士 你不配死在我战锤之下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:34.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,化为碎片消散吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.28,0:17:44.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.87,0:17:52.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,切 大只的玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:53.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是史尔基
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.50,0:17:55.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,婆婆没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:01.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要进到哪里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:04.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,到底有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.52,0:18:08.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:28.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这可真是要命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:31.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就像史尔基说的 伤口裂开了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:33.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我处理不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:37.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 这样就算穿上那个也动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:40.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,拖拖拉拉的 火就要烧过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.59,0:18:45.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,的确现在这个状态穿上那个还能保命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.34,0:18:46.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.93,0:18:51.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女 魔女在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.06,0:18:53.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 是那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:55.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多要告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:57.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,您慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.23,0:19:00.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这里果然还是要靠的我的魔法撑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.70,0:19:04.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是把大家卷入危险的我的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:12.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.17,0:19:13.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真的要这么做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.33,0:19:16.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,给伤成这样的格斯穿上甲胄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:19.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,现在只能相信史尔基了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:21.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 我不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:31.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,来了 怪兽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:37.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,耍小聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.02,0:19:40.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,躲在那里了 黑色剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.94,0:19:43.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今还要丑态百出吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:54.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,救我 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:55.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,明明吃下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.78,0:19:57.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,明明应该咬死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.19,0:20:16.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.29,0:20:34.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:44.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这不光是厉害了 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.05,0:20:46.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才还都站不起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.22,0:20:50.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你这就不厚道了 这么厉害的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.18,0:20:53.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在退治兽鬼的时候就该给他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:57.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这个不是那么简单的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:20:59.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.02,0:21:03.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,从动作上看完全变了个人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.48,0:21:06.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 那把剑确实是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:07.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:13.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,很怀念啊 老友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.52,0:21:17.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,也要让他踏上同样的道路吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.75,0:21:20.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,和你一样化为冥府魔道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.75,0:21:24.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这甲胄是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.67,0:21:30.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,穿上的时候 伤口就像假的一样不痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.80,0:21:36.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这都无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.06,0:21:39.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,疼痛都 无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:41.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这些
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:47.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这股在体内沸腾的冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.18,0:21:52.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身体中有什么 狂暴的东西涌现出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.45,0:21:54.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,献 上 身 体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.62,0:21:55.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.27,0:21:56.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,献 上 血 肉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.91,0:21:57.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.66,0:21:59.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,献 上 一 切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.50,0:22:01.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.13,0:22:02.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,献 上 骨 髓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:05.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,献上你的一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.84,0:22:09.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,献 上 生 命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.64,0:22:14.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,甲胄的形状
